&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="图形化aria2下载">图形化aria2下载
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="termux在本地搭建aria2ariang">Termux在本地搭建Aria2+AriaNg
&lt;/h3>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>下载需要的Packages&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pkg in wget unzip aria2 tmux
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="2">
&lt;li>下载Caddy&lt;br>
这样因为Caddy配置起来比较容易,所以用Caddy当HTTP Server.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cd~
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">wget -qO- https://getcaddy.com | bash -s personal
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;ol start="3">
&lt;li>下载AriaNg并解压&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
